  "text": "Existing compressed matrix formats with good performance like CSR-VI [CITATION_1] similarly show only moderate compression ratios. In contrast, our approach builds upon research on lightweight database compression, such as compressed bitmaps and dictionary coding, as well as sparse matrix representations.",
